</li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFOwen_Bowcott2003" class="citation web cs1">Owen Bowcott (18 August 2003). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2003/aug/18/uk.religion">"Row over Vatican order to conceal priests' sex abuse"</a>. <i>the Guardian</i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=the+Guardian&amp;rft.atitle=Row+over+Vatican+order+to+conceal+priests%27+sex+abuse&amp;rft.date=2003-08-18&amp;rft.au=Owen+Bowcott&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2003%2Faug%2F18%2Fuk.religion&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACrimen+sollicitationis" class="Z3988"></span></span>
