<li id="cite_note-Doyle-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Doyle_13-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.awrsipe.com/doyle/2008/2008-10-03-Commentary-on-1922-and-1962-documents.pdf">Thomas Doyle, <i>The 1922 instruction and the 1962 instruction "</i>Crimen sollicitationis<i>" promulgated by the Vatican</i></a></span>
